appeng.api.storage

Interface IMEInventoryHandler<T extends IAEStack<T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Superinterfaces:
    IMEInventory<T>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICellInventoryHandler<T>, IMEMonitor<T>, IPortableCell

    public interface IMEInventoryHandler<T extends IAEStack<T>>
extends IMEInventory<T>
    Thin logic layer that can be swapped with different IMEInventory implementations, used to handle features related to storage, that are Separate from the storage medium itself.
